. This is a laid back town. This is 45 KM from Madanapalli. The place is very scenic and has a rural flavour.

Buses: Number of buses available from Madanapalli,Tirupathi,Chittoor,Palamaner,Rayachoti.
Trains:Currently one train runs between Tirupathi and Gunthakal via Kalikiri.The number is going to increase over a period. 
Fly: Nearest air port Tirupathi( 2 hours) and Bangalore(3 hours)

If you like trekking, then there are many hills around, mainly Ankalamma konda which is good to climb with pleasant environment.

Nearest scenic places of visit: Horsley hills, Thalakona forest and water fall.
